":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T00:04:44.000Z","msg":"最感動：買完機票先知要midterm，以為佢會鬧爆我，點知反而安慰我。<br />\n<br />\n最痛：暫時無"},{"pid":"1d9afb335b5263bd62821125a04e2f28030b2676","tid":1497044,"uid":32380,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T00:08:47.000Z","msg":"應該冇嘢痛過出軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2ecdd58dafd6030ce94a8a7cb96cf498dcc39f5","tid":1497044,"uid":247639,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T00:13:26.000Z","msg":"最痛：冇Ex"},{"pid":"5e75f32d2be204de9a3eb5b722acefda60bc884d","tid":1497044,"uid":293799,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T01:09:28.000Z","msg":"最感動 ： 每年冬天都會織頸巾俾我，試過冬天企係到等我2個鐘<br />\n<br />\n最痛：個陣返學返朝9晚6 夜晚11至朝7返工 做左2個月<br />\n累到沖緊涼 返緊工 都會訓著。每日只係會訓2個鐘就要出門口 到我頂唔順遲辭唔返工 搵另一份輕鬆d既工 佢會話我冇上進心 唔捱得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n分左手之後 一個星期同另一個一齊"},{"pid":"cea8c4918be9bc4a98b3a7a0516d93b97f494c0b","tid":1497044,"uid":75013,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T02:43:21.000Z","msg":"最感動：好努力追我 堅持不懈<br />\n最痛：一次又一次踩我底線 越黎越冷淡 逼我講分手"},{"pid":"1cc309bbd2b14deb71dc80134dd9d12e56098fd0","tid":1497044,"uid":153422,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T02:49:52.000Z","msg":"最感動：真係冇，因為個ex好公主病，日日好似湊女咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最難過：日日都好難過，最難聽嘅說話係：「因為你係我男朋友，所以我有咩缺點你都要接受」，DLLM，真係難聽過粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad9abbd5477db4ee457cc3d1706ce920ed39dd48","tid":1497044,"uid":206687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1cc309bbd2b14deb71dc80134dd9d12e56098fd0","tid":1497044,"uid":153422,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T02:49:52.000Z","msg":"最感動：真係冇，因為個ex好公主病，日日好似湊女咁<img src=\"