 />"},{"pid":"cf0fbf327044fa0528ddfcf7be01fe7b284d7c44","tid":1497044,"uid":4803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T18:09:01.000Z","msg":"收皮啦 屌你老母"},{"pid":"dbeacc5ed60b87f518396046e00fb1e0ed6ca9b4","tid":1497044,"uid":238769,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T19:08:27.000Z","msg":"最感動: 每逢係學校通頂都會買野食俾我，冬天又會買暖包俾我。<br />\n<br />\n最難過: 一齊成年幾從來無心裝載過我講過既野，永遠做錯事或者唔記得野，都會搵理由同藉口應付我就當冇佐件事，就算我費盡心思教佢或者解釋，無論我打幾多字定到最後真係忍唔住提出分手都好，佢都只係覆我一個唔開心既emoji或者唔超過10個字既句字就算。"},{"pid":"545455efe4b62bd0f062e1f7b70ac288c40baae0","tid":1497044,"uid":161537,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T19:24:51.000Z","msg":"最感動... <br />\n<br />\n諗唔到，到底係佢失敗定我失敗？"},{"pid":"08d794a8d0726df40dba1d7381600a2744f984cc","tid":1497044,"uid":165510,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T19:40:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba2218071aabd37a539259a4aafc1f1e419d1e2","tid":1497044,"uid":88491,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T21:04:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}